English: Subject will get more out of MediPacks.
Description:
Don't localize MediPacks.
Describes the advantage of having a good "med efficiency" value. Essentially this means that when the subject uses a MediPack, it will replenish more health than usual.

French.Translation: Le sujet tire plus de bénéfices des MediPacks.

Italian.Translation: Il soggetto otterrà benefici maggiori dai MediPack.

Spanish.Translation: El sujeto les sacará más partido a los botiquines.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: O indivíduo é mais beneficiado pelos pacotes médicos.

Polish.Translation: Biorca odzyska więcej zdrowia po użyciu apteczki.

Japanese.Translation: 対象へのMediPacksの効果が上がる。

Korean.Translation: 대상이 구급팩 효과를 더 많이 받습니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 實驗對象將從醫藥包[MediPack]獲益較多。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 医药包治疗使用者的效果提高。
